Sat Feb 12 15:13:12 CET 2000
	* texmf release 1.0.2 (TETEXDOC.ps regenerated with dvips -G0 ...)

Tue Feb  1 15:08:34 CET 2000 te
	* src release 1.0.7, texmf release 1.0.1

Wed Jul  7 08:05:09 CEST 1999 te
	* 1.0.6 release
	* mfw is build with support for the X Windows System by default
	* bugfix to improve kpathsea debugging (spaces go to log file
	  instead of terminal)
	* don't permit disk searches in TEXMFMAIN by default (texmf.cnf
	  change)
	* fix order of -I flags for the C compiler to prevent problems
	  with conflicting files installed in system directories
	* changes to texconfig to make it more robust
	* xdvik now uses on_exit if atexit is not available (e.g. SunOS)
	* cleanup for cyrillic in fmtutil.in (just comments)

Wed Jun 16 07:53:55 CEST 1999 te
	* correct broken fix from last xdvik patch
	* strip binaries for install-exec target
	* install kpathsea header files for install-exec target
	* avoid installing mktex.opt etc. for install-exec target
	* rename strcasestr -> ht_strcasestr in libwww to avoid problems
	with existing strcasestr function
	* change strdup -> xstrdup in xdvi.c, because not all systems
	have strdup

Sat Jun 12 13:15:34 CEST 1999 te
	* fix serious bug about tmpfile handling in xdvik.

Fri Jun 11 15:03:16 CEST 1999 te
	* portability fix in libs/ncurses/ncurses/lib_napms.c

